              <section class="card">
                <h2>Write for the Library</h2>
                <p>Find support for creating content and writing effectively on behalf of the library.</p>
                 <ul class="card-links visual-elements">
                  <li><a href="/content/voice-and-tone/"><span class="material-symbols-rounded content" aria-hidden="true">ink_pen</span><span>Voice and tone</span></a></li>
                  <li><a href="/content/writing-about-the-library/"><span class="material-symbols-rounded content" aria-hidden="true">ink_pen</span><span>Writing about the library</span></a></li>
                </ul>
